    "description": "MakeMyTrip Consulting Pvt Ltd has an exciting opening for a Software Engineer at our Allahabad office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout MakeMyTrip Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nMakeMyTrip Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in React\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Allahabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with MakeMyTrip Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
